room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by The Art of Escape: ICT in Wichita
room_description: The Syndicate has recruited you for a very important job: you will be robbing one of the largest banks in the country, The International Bank of Paradise. The Syndicate team has gotten you past the lobby and into the Bank Manager, Lillian Stevens' office, where the vault awaits you. Now it's up to you to decipher the clues and solve all of the puzzles to get into the vault.
